description: Theta series of Niemeier lattice of type A_1^24.
references: J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, "Sphere Packings, Lattices and Groups", Springer-Verlag, p. 407.
formula: This series is the q-expansion of 11/18*E_4(z)^3 + 7/18*E_6(z)^2. Cf. A004009, A013973. - Daniel D. Briggs, Nov 26 2011
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
